author: Diane
title: Diane
text: Booking was a pleasure. Mel couldn't have been more pleasant & helpful, keeping in touch with me as to what was happening & persisting until she managed to get the flights I required. Tickets were promptly booked & supplied along with all information required immediately. I acan thorougly recommend them.
